snippet.title: Amber Heard Lied: The Smoking Gun Clip Exposing the #MeToo Playbook to #CancelCulture Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
In Episode 3 of the video podcast - The Respondent - Greg exposes Amber Heard's  #MeToo playbook. Register now: https://www.thinkspot.com/event_signup?event=NQuxyP

#MenToo pioneer and men's right activists Bettina Arndt joins the show. Janice Fiamengo joins for a live Q&A after the episode. This all kicks off on Sunday, July 19th, at 1:00 p.m. Pacific Time on thinkspot. Register here: https://www.thinkspot.com/event_signu...
